  "texts": [
    "In the two solution trees in Figure 9, S4 and S8 are marked as \"Pass\", while S2, S7, and S8 are marked as \"Match\".",
    "Therefore, only S8 has a reward of R(S8)=1.",
    "For the i-th round of solution S, its reward score R(S_i) is the highest reward score among all the solutions to which it belongs.",
    "Taking C1 inFigure 9 as an example, C1 belongs to both solution S3 and solution S4.",
    "Since R(S4)=-2 and R(S3)=-3, R(C1|A1)=-2."
  ],
